data.description: TURN KEY IN TORINO! This 4/2/2 2021 Groza Builders Custom Home has Everything You Could Want and is Filled with Modern Finishes. The Home Boasts Wood-Plank Tile Floors throughout all Main Living Areas and Bathrooms, a Formal Dining Room, and Stylish Lighting and Fans. This Kitchen is a Cook's Dream! SS Appliances, White Cabinets, White Quartz Countertops, Oversized Pantry, Sink Equipped w/ Reverse Osmosis System, and an Amazing View to the Living Room and Spacious Yard. Relax in your Large Master Bedroom with Custom Feature Wall, Walk-In Closet and Stunning Master Bathroom Complete w/ Contemporary Tile, Lighting, Cabinetry, Soaker Tub & Walk-In Shower. The Secondary Bathroom includes a White Quartz Countertop w/ Dual Sinks and a Tub w/ Floor to Ceiling Tile. The 3 Secondary Bedrooms are Well-Sized w/ Large Closets for Storage. New Matching Washer Dryer Set are Included and there is an Additional Closet for Laundry Items. There is Plenty of Room for a Pool in your Backyard, Lined with Trees for Privacy. Complete with Impact Windows and Doors this Home Has it All! Located on a Quiet Street, Minutes from St Lucie West Shops and Restaurants, Mets Stadium, Close to Tradition, and Easy Access to 1-95 & Crosstown Pkwy. Why Wait to Build?! Call Today to Schedule a Private Showing.
